solutions.content:
**Solution 1: Linear time & O(n) space**
A linear time solution by precomputing the prefix sums before attempting to find the pivot index.
- iterate over the array once to precompute the prefix sums for each index
- at every iteration of i
	- check if the sum before  and after `i` are the same

```
var pivotIndex = function (nums) {
    //1. Calculate prefix sums before attempting to find the pivot
    const prefix_sums = []
    let sum = 0;
    for(num of nums){
        sum += num;
        prefix_sums.push(sum)
    }

    //2. Find pivot index
    for(let i=0; i < nums.length; i++){
        const sum_before_i = prefix_sums[i-1] || 0; // 0 is for when i=0 & we get undefined
        const sum_after_i  = prefix_sums[nums.length-1] - prefix_sums[i]
        if(sum_before_i === sum_after_i) return i;
    }
    return -1;
};
```


**Solution 2: Linear time**
- iterate 1 time to get the sum of the entire array
- iterate over the array to find th pivot
	- on each iteration, subtract `total_sum` by `nums[i]` to give us our "suffix sum" (sum after i)
	- check if the prefix sum is equal to the suffix sum


```
var pivotIndex = function (nums) {
    let prefix_sum = 0;
    let total_sum = nums.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0)

    for (let i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
        total_sum -= nums[i] // after we subtract, the sum after i

        if (prefix_sum === total_sum) return i
        prefix_sum += nums[i]
    }

    return -1
};
```



**Solution 3: Brute force**
- slowest solution
- at every iteration find the sum before and after i and make the comparison

```
var pivotIndex = function (nums) {
    let pivot_index = -1;

    for(let i=0; i < nums.length; i++){
        // Calculate sum before i
        let sum_before_i = 0;
        for(let j=0; j < i; j++){
            sum_before_i += nums[j]
        }

        // Calculate sum after i
        let sum_after_i = 0
        for (let j= i+1; j < nums.length; j++) {
            sum_after_i += nums[j];
        }
        if(sum_before_i === sum_after_i) return i;
    }
    return pivot_index;
};
```

